{"tid":1906420,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"明星餐廳生意慘淡相繼停業","createTime":"2020-03-02T02:37:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T09:39:42.000Z","uid":184679,"like":333,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":116,"replies":[{"pid":"85e716cd994d861777ac7441527579bb378038b0","tid":1906420,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T02:37:19.000Z","msg":"全港飲食業因新冠肺炎而步入寒冬，藝人所開的明星店亦不能倖免，周杰倫、謝霆鋒、張敬軒的食店都暫停營業，甚至關門大吉，黃宗澤和陳豪所經營的蠔吧及咖啡店的生意大跌八成，小店為求生存，轉型增設外賣，使出食飯送口罩的招數來吸客，個個都咬緊牙關頂下去，希望捱得一日得一日！<br />\n<br />\n在疫情的陰霾下，人人自危，為免增加染病風險，盡量避免外出，飲食生意一落千丈，不少食店都面對結業的危機，由於曾經有人打邊爐聚餐時確診，令火鍋店成為高危地點之一。<br />\n<br />\n周董霆鋒相繼遭殃<br />\n<br />\n由台灣天王周杰倫(Jay)與友人所開的「J-pot」亦遭殃，2月中開始暫停營業，目前會視乎疫情進展，初步預計會於3月1日恢復營業，而跟Jay一樣暫停營業的還有張敬軒(軒仔)的餅店，隸屬軒仔投資的「仙后餐廳」餅店Patisserie早於2月10日暫停營業，而總店「仙后餐廳」仍然正常營業。<br />\n<br />\n謝霆鋒選擇壯士斷臂，成立的曲奇品牌《12道鋒味》曾於中環、尖沙咀等多個地方開設分店，在疫情影響下，所有店舖都關門大吉，目前只會不定時以短期租約形式開Pop Up Store，霆鋒亦決定轉戰網上銷售市場，開創一個全新的網上平台，身為老板的他亦將會現身於社交平台幫忙宣傳。<br />\n<br />\n黃宗澤蠔吧得兩枱客<br />\n<br />\n在逆境之下，藝人誓與店鋪共存，唯有諗計求存，黃宗澤（Bosco）投資的蠔吧「Oystermine」，去年由九龍城擴充搬到尖沙嘴，疫情影響下生意額大跌七、八成，記者曾走訪該店，發現下午時段只得兩枱顧客，客人亦刻意挑選了門外空氣比較流通的露天位置，餐廳門外貼了告示，表明餐廳會四小時進行清潔消毒一次，店內職員各人都戴上口罩，做足安全措施。<br />\n<br />\n對於生意額大跌，Bosco說沒辦法，自己會盡量頂下去，跟員工一起想對策，盡量縮減成本及開支，以前全年無休，現時會彈性處理，正在研究淡靜的日子不開鋪，員工更向他提出自願放無薪假，目前有二十個員工，由經理安排他們放假，至於自救的方法，Bosco說任何方法都會用，現時正與業主商談減租問題，希望業主答允共度時艱。<br />\n<br />\n陳豪減人手傾減租<br />\n<br />\n陳豪(Mo)位於尖沙嘴K11 Musea的咖啡店「Blooms Coffee」，疫情發生之前，每日都人頭湧湧，大排長龍，如今只有一枱客人，非常慘淡，而店員由平日的四個減至只得兩個，Mo說生意有一定的影響，正與業主商討減租，生意跌幅非常大，笑言自己好傷，幸咖啡店的防守性比較強，盡量咬緊牙關捱過去，由於員工只得四個，人手並不多，所以不會裁員。<br />\n<br />\n江若琳經營的貓酒店的營業額跌足7成，單月損失十萬元，幸好得一眾客戶支持，業主又願意減租，齊齊共度時艱，她表示會堅持下去，所有員工每日上班都要戴口罩和量體溫，貓酒店會加強清潔和消毒，務求令每位客人放心，同時都會「出招」吸客，推出全單八折的優惠，並售賣貓的健康食品和周邊產品來增加收入，希望能捱過今次難關。<br />\n<br />\n吳日言三星期做六百元生意<br />\n<br />\n吳日言(Yan)開設的飯糰店《幸福。駅》在一年內開設了3間店舖，曾試過所有店舖全日都無生意，最淒慘是山頂店，三個星期只做了六百元生意，只能用慘不忍睹來形容，所以Yan決定暫時關閉山頂店，另外兩間分店就正與業主洽談減租方案。<br />\n<br />\n學生是Yan午市的其中一項重要生意來源，一再將學生開課日推遲至4月20日，令她的生意雪上加霜，唯有變陣主攻外賣，推出外賣便當外，更新增便當送貨服務，現時很多大集團的食肆開門大吉，Yan看準這個時機，尋找土瓜灣和觀塘兩間位置較好的舖來擴充業務，實行人棄我取，認為反而是一個商機，慶幸的是受市況影響，業主願意簽下兩年的租約上減兩成半的租金，Yan希望能與員工和香港市民大眾一起度過這次難關，一起走出谷底見青天。<br />\n<br />\n胡諾言（胡仔）投資過百萬，與弟弟開設自助式快餐店Kitchen Bros，生意額大跌一半，慶幸到會生意額上升，拉上補下才可以繼續經營，胡仔指快餐店主要做早、午餐，客人以OL為主，這個時勢大家也選擇留在家中，門市銷情一定有影響，幸好弟弟即時「出招」，為客人提供到會服務，送上簡便住家餸，賣點是星級味道，經濟價錢，還有西湯及甜品，只要在家加熱就可食用，而且全部獨立包裝，大家食得安心，大受客人歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n杜大偉送口罩吸客<br />\n<br />\n吳啟明的中菜餐廳「慢煮兩餐」，生意好的時候，客人想訂位也訂不到，受疫情影響，生意大跌七成，他透露租約快將約滿，若然業主不肯減租，餐廳考慮結業。之前變陣想出共享餐廳計畫，有些餐廳、酒吧不做午市，可以租用場地來增加生意額，剛試行兩個月，誰知又來個疫症，根本沒有人出街，宣傳都無用，目前只有靠外賣，主力為大公司提供外賣飯盒，而晚市有客人預約才會開鋪，不過，飯始終要食，他正與飲食集團密謀合作計畫，透過網上訂餐，將外賣出品送到某區自取，他抱着香港人堅強、拼搏、不屈的精神，嘗試不同方法，希望闖出新的血路。<br />\n<br />\n杜大偉（David）與表哥及倫哥開設的倫哥私房菜，因主力是打邊爐關係，生意大跌九成，目前五家分店中，只有觀塘店營業，除加強食肆消毒工作外，還推出入座即送韓國高質素口罩來防疫，被客人大讚有綽頭，David亦會努力拓展外賣生意，之前已推出「懶人雞煲」、燉湯及佛跳牆等菜式，正努力構思更多能夠外賣的產品。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hd.stheadline.com/life/ent/realtime/1712907/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82-%E7%96%AB%E5%A2%83%E9%9B%A3%E6%8D%B1%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%BC%E7%9C%BC%E6%B7%9A-%E6%98%8E%E6%98%9F%E9%A4%90%E5%BB%B3%E7%94%9F%E6%84%8F%E6%85%98%E6%B7%A1%E7%9B%B8%E7%B9%BC%E5%81%9C%E6%A5%AD</code></pre>"},{"pid":"d4ee9b17e8788e9f77cd5bdf85ade31994e50f30","tid":1906420,"uid":126621,"like":532,"dislike":23,"score":509,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T02:39:37.000Z","msg":"全部都無係運動出過聲<br />\n抵撚死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲話傾減租<br />\n傾你老母咩"},{"pid":"0a71b9a838b2f44b53324e14368b073d7227ff62","tid":1906420,"uid":127575,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T02:40:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1b891f07aef20cee10c851dd2dbd4ad5e3b24db","tid":1906420,"uid":228143,"like":134,"dislike":0,"score":134,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T02:41:14.000Z","msg":"明星有撚用咩  而家去食野唔係去睇星 j女<br />\n<br />\n難食自然冇人食嫁啦<br />\n<br />\n又唔見堅石燒時代冇人食"},{"pid":"78f2512033a1b232b3a1e428cf161839b075779f","tid":1906420,"uid":165450,"like":197,"dislike":2,"score":195,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T02:41:32.000Z","msg":"重有間垃圾 燉呢 幾時執 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd38b63ae60c1489bff5365c6ed664152425ca3f","tid":1906420,"uid":179967,"like":59,"dislike":1,"score":58,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T02:49:16.000Z","msg":"人地連鎖酒樓同餐廳都捱唔住 憑咩你明星餐廳捱到?"},{"pid":"8cda83f4cfe4883ae0865f607c60223609e15306","tid":1906420,"uid":6103,"like":199,"dislike":6,"score":193,"quote":{"pid":"d4ee9b17e8788e9f77cd5bdf85ade31994e50f30","tid":1906420,"uid":126621,"like":532,"dislike":23,"score":509,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T02:39:37.000Z","msg":"全部都無係運動出過聲<br />\n抵撚死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲話傾減租<br />\n傾你老母咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T02:52:53.000Z","msg":"吳啟明間餐廳有罷過市<br />\n有貼過連農牆"},{"pid":"4a17a81439b0d0d5e471642b9c0c4bc664635be8","tid":1906420,"uid":224533,"like":62,"dislike":1,"score":61,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T03:34:14.000Z","msg":"明星效應喺飲食業係冇用，食物質素同價錢決定一切"},{"pid":"a1fb1cf6a44d9607527a0602848322c022e63927","tid":1906420,"uid":156376,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T03:37:22.000Z","msg":"錢就識得賺，香港有難時唔幫手，抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9b83e551cf58cee2ff28f73aac3fb77e6055e0f","tid":1906420,"uid":8308,"like":113,"dislike":1,"score":112,"quote":{"pid":"4a17a81439b0d0d5e471642b9c0c4bc664635be8","tid":1906420,"uid":224533,"like":62,"dislike":1,"score":61,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T03:34:14.000Z","msg":"明星效應喺飲食業係冇用，食物質素同價錢決定一切"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T03:38:59.000Z","msg":"如果個明星心地好 <br />\n個效應就會好高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> eg. 譚小環"},{"pid":"7e7aba38138685fcbdc6d546593d2cf0f2a35fdd","tid":1906420,"uid":11080,"like":186,"dislike":2,"score":184,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T03:53:47.000Z","msg":"幸福。駅 <br />\n黃店黎...唔好食華御結啦"},{"pid":"e19e6e98382b328ee080bf4cf83d918a3324c9f6","tid":1906420,"uid":86756,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T03:56:11.000Z","msg":"Blooms 陳豪間店本身真係日日大排長龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？？"},{"pid":"2780aa44542c8443912dba66852370b8b87be061","tid":1906420,"uid":57674,"like":231,"dislike":3,"score":228,"quote":{"pid":"d4ee9b17e8788e9f77cd5bdf85ade31994e50f30","tid":1906420,"uid":126621,"like":532,"dislike":23,"score":509,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T02:39:37.000Z","msg":"全部都無係運動出過聲<br />\n抵撚死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲話傾減租<br />\n傾你老母咩"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T03:58:59.000Z","msg":"我印象吳日言好似接受過蘋果訪問+有出過聲"},{"pid":"100aef1f82940ffda8f02ba6fce20a583ed6baec","tid":1906420,"uid":211466,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T03:59:39.000Z","msg":"明星?<br />\n撐警人士?"},{"pid":"e31d34f7e574c555bf430e9f03a0d087d29f8d86","tid":1906420,"uid":2772,"like":11,"dislike":106,"score":-95,"quote":{"pid":"7e7aba38138685fcbdc6d546593d2cf0f2a35fdd","tid":1906420,"uid":11080,"like":186,"dislike":2,"score":184,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T03:53:47.000Z","msg":"幸福。駅 <br />\n黃店黎...唔好食華御結啦"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T04:04:01.000Z","msg":"唉...<br />\n你既然問到<br />\n我就認真答你<br />\n<br />\n首先,咩係「初弒」?<br />\n初次弒父,弒母?你明唔明弒字點解?<br />\n仲有個「魂」字又同「初弒」有咩關係?<br />\n你老母個靈魂初次俾你殺左?<br />\n最重要既一點係,點解要加個「。」係中間?<br />\n<br />\n總結你個名唔單只on9,仲1999,九唔答八<br />\n唔好講個型字,柒字都談不上"},{"pid":"6caca4827bba7755ee6599f495868ae0b0860de2","tid":1906420,"uid":42982,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T04:05:13.000Z","msg":"譚小環你又唔報下？"},{"pid":"c9a48149986bc972d53ac964e5c0c3f4704ae26e","tid":1906420,"uid":304160,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"85e716cd994d861777ac7441527579bb378038b0","tid":1906420,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T02:37:19.000Z","msg":"全港飲食業因新冠肺炎而步入寒冬，藝人所開的明星店亦不能倖免，周杰倫、謝霆鋒、張敬軒的食店都暫停營業，甚至關門大吉，黃宗澤和陳豪所經營的蠔吧及咖啡店的生意大跌八成，小店為求生存，轉型增設外賣，使出食飯送口罩的招數來吸客，個個都咬緊牙關頂下去，希望捱得一日得一日！<br />\n<br />\n在疫情的陰霾下，人人自危，為免增加染病風險，盡量避免外出，飲食生意一落千丈，不少食店都面對結業的危機，由於曾經有人打邊爐聚餐時確診，令火鍋店成為高危地點之一。<br />\n<br />\n周董霆鋒相繼遭殃<br />\n<br />\n由台灣天王周杰倫(Jay)與友人所開的「J-pot」亦遭殃，2月中開始暫停營業，目前會視乎疫情進展，初步預計會於3月1日恢復營業，而跟Jay一樣暫停營業的還有張敬軒(軒仔)的餅店，隸屬軒仔投資的「仙后餐廳」餅店Patisserie早於2月10日暫停營業，而總店「仙后餐廳」仍然正常營業。<br />\n<br />\n謝霆鋒選擇壯士斷臂，成立的曲奇品牌《12道鋒味》曾於中環、尖沙咀等多個地方開設分店，在疫情影響下，所有店舖都關門大吉，目前只會不定時以短期租約形式開Pop Up Store，霆鋒亦決定轉戰網上銷售市場，開創一個全新的網上平台，身為老板的他亦將會現身於社交平台幫忙宣傳。<br />\n<br />\n黃宗澤蠔吧得兩枱客<br />\n<br />\n在逆境之下，藝人誓與店鋪共存，唯有諗計求存，黃宗澤（Bosco）投資的蠔吧「Oystermine」，去年由九龍城擴充搬到尖沙嘴，疫情影響下生意額大跌七、八成，記者曾走訪該店，發現下午時段只得兩枱顧客，客人亦刻意挑選了門外空氣比較流通的露天位置，餐廳門外貼了告示，表明餐廳會四小時進行清潔消毒一次，店內職員各人都戴上口罩，做足安全措施。<br />\n<br />\n對於生意額大跌，Bosco說沒辦法，自己會盡量頂下去，跟員工一起想對策，盡量縮減成本及開支，以前全年無休，現時會彈性處理，正在研究淡靜的日子不開鋪，員工更向他提出自願放無薪假，目前有二十個員工，由經理安排他們放假，至於自救的方法，Bosco說任何方法都會用，現時正與業主商談減租問題，希望業主答允共度時艱。<br />\n<br />\n陳豪減人手傾減租<br />\n<br />\n陳豪(Mo)位於尖沙嘴K11 Musea的咖啡店「Blooms Coffee」，疫情發生之前，每日都人頭湧湧，大排長龍，如今只有一枱客人，非常慘淡，而店員由平日的四個減至只得兩個，Mo說生意有一定的影響，正與業主商討減租，生意跌幅非常大，笑言自己好傷，幸咖啡店的防守性比較強，盡量咬緊牙關捱過去，由於員工只得四個，人手並不多，所以不會裁員。<br />\n<br />\n江若琳經營的貓酒店的營業額跌足7成，單月損失十萬元，幸好得一眾客戶支持，業主又願意減租，齊齊共度時艱，她表示會堅持下去，所有員工每日上班都要戴口罩和量體溫，貓酒店會加強清潔和消毒，務求令每位客人放心，同時都會「出招」吸客，推出全單八折的優惠，並售賣貓的健康食品和周邊產品來增加收入，希望能捱過今次難關。<br />\n<br />\n吳日言三星期做六百元生意<br />\n<br />\n吳日言(Yan)開設的飯糰店《幸福。駅》在一年內開設了3間店舖，曾試過所有店舖全日都無生意，最淒慘是山頂店，三個星期只做了六百元生意，只能用慘不忍睹來形容，所以Yan決定暫時關閉山頂店，另外兩間分店就正與業主洽談減租方案。<br />\n<br />\n學生是Yan午市的其中一項重要生意來源，一再將學生開課日推遲至4月20日，令她的生意雪上加霜，唯有變陣主攻外賣，推出外賣便當外，更新增便當送貨服務，現時很多大集團的食肆開門大吉，Yan看準這個時機，尋找土瓜灣和觀塘兩間位置較好的舖來擴充業務，實行人棄我取，認為反而是一個商機，慶幸的是受市況影響，業主願意簽下兩年的租約上減兩成半的租金，Yan希望能與員工和香港市民大眾一起度過這次難關，一起走出谷底見青天。<br />\n<br />\n胡諾言（胡仔）投資過百萬，與弟弟開設自助式快餐店Kitchen Bros，生意額大跌一半，慶幸到會生意額上升，拉上補下才可以繼續經營，胡仔指快餐店主要做早、午餐，客人以OL為主，這個時勢大家也選擇留在家中，門市銷情一定有影響，幸好弟弟即時「出招」，為客人提供到會服務，送上簡便住家餸，賣點是星級味道，經濟價錢，還有西湯及甜品，只要在家加熱就可食用，而且全部獨立包裝，大家食得安心，大受客人歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n杜大偉送口罩吸客<br />\n<br />\n吳啟明的中菜餐廳「慢煮兩餐」，生意好的時候，客人想訂位也訂不到，受疫情影響，生意大跌七成，他透露租約快將約滿，若然業主不肯減租，餐廳考慮結業。之前變陣想出共享餐廳計畫，有些餐廳、酒吧不做午市，可以租用場地來增加生意額，剛試行兩個月，誰知又來個疫症，根本沒有人出街，宣傳都無用，目前只有靠外賣，主力為大公司提供外賣飯盒，而晚市有客人預約才會開鋪，不過，飯始終要食，他正與飲食集團密謀合作計畫，透過網上訂餐，將外賣出品送到某區自取，他抱着香港人堅強、拼搏、不屈的精神，嘗試不同方法，希望闖出新的血路。<br />\n<br />\n杜大偉（David）與表哥及倫哥開設的倫哥私房菜，因主力是打邊爐關係，生意大跌九成，目前五家分店中，只有觀塘店營業，除加強食肆消毒工作外，還推出入座即送韓國高質素口罩來防疫，被客人大讚有綽頭，David亦會努力拓展外賣生意，之前已推出「懶人雞煲」、燉湯及佛跳牆等菜式，正努力構思更多能夠外賣的產品。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hd.stheadline.com/life/ent/realtime/1712907/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82-%E7%96%AB%E5%A2%83%E9%9B%A3%E6%8D%B1%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%BC%E7%9C%BC%E6%B7%9A-%E6%98%8E%E6%98%9F%E9%A4%90%E5%BB%B3%E7%94%9F%E6%84%8F%E6%85%98%E6%B7%A1%E7%9B%B8%E7%B9%BC%E5%81%9C%E6%A5%AD</code></pre>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T04:08:52.000Z","msg":"胡諾賢成日係無線拍大灣區唔去大灣區開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd2425f748106b5a53f037cfce860b404fd8db5f","tid":1906420,"uid":11080,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"e31d34f7e574c555bf430e9f03a0d087d29f8d86","tid":1906420,"uid":2772,"like":11,"dislike":106,"score":-95,"quote":{"pid":"7e7aba38138685fcbdc6d546593d2cf0f2a35fdd","tid":1906420,"uid":11080,"like":186,"dislike":2,"score":184,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T03:53:47.000Z","msg":"幸福。駅 <br />\n黃店黎...唔好食華御結啦"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T04:04:01.000Z","msg":"唉...<br />\n你既然問到<br />\n我就認真答你<br />\n<br />\n首先,咩係「初弒」?<br />\n初次弒父,弒母?你明唔明弒字點解?<br />\n仲有個「魂」字又同「初弒」有咩關係?<br />\n你老母個靈魂初次俾你殺左?<br />\n最重要既一點係,點解要加個「。」係中間?<br />\n<br />\n總結你個名唔單只on9,仲1999,九唔答八<br />\n唔好講個型字,柒字都談不上"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T04:08:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c55e191a716d3aa980d0ab9e88927620f951465","tid":1906420,"uid":146621,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"78f2512033a1b232b3a1e428cf161839b075779f","tid":1906420,"uid":165450,"like":197,"dislike":2,"score":195,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T02:41:32.000Z","msg":"重有間垃圾 燉呢 幾時執 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T04:11:46.000Z","msg":"奀星<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />