TFnLRhO0hL0igQy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=edb50054\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2418715/【反修例】「丁旺蟹」吳啟明響應8.5罷工%E3%80%80中環新店設連儂門為市民打氣</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DrC1iPw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDrC1iPw.png&h=fdb20a7a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZNm9sHS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZNm9sHS.png&h=dc334305&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過新年個排<br />\n比人發現佢舖頭貼左&lt;&lt;家有囍事2020&gt;&gt;poster<br />\n所以都有人屌 大家自己判斷"},{"pid":"1b343984c777d55b7d1ef63b0bb1d9488d363d2f","tid":1906420,"uid":171643,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"a1fb1cf6a44d9607527a0602848322c022e63927","tid":1906420,"uid":156376,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T03:37:22.000Z","msg":"錢就識得賺，香港有難時唔幫手，抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T12:27:58.000Z","msg":"吳日言黃店黎"},{"pid":"7cc3de127eb25344120a211ba01a3507b5314aaf","tid":1906420,"uid":251086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T12:29:14.000Z","msg":"成績表"},{"pid":"5ad22c21c98c7faf9f385c4bcb43d4160ac55bd4","tid":1906420,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e7aba38138685fcbdc6d546593d2cf0f2a35fdd","tid":1906420,"uid":11080,"like":186,"dislike":2,"score":184,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T03:53:47.000Z","msg":"幸福。駅 <br />\n黃店黎...唔好食華御結啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T12:32:28.000Z","msg":"深水埗開幸福駅都係吳日言嘅？"},{"pid":"c59f07e615c9274e7f4baaf2e1362b79d4df5270","tid":1906420,"uid":173817,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T12:37:38.000Z","msg":"明星邊撚到明ar. who??"},{"pid":"68bf35ccb5a7985d3b4fa845e7237c90393edf4e","tid":1906420,"uid":55496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T12:41:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fac